ating provider up to a maximum of a  40 match per month  to receive the full  40 monthly match you will have to contribute  80 per month    40 per semi monthly pay period   to your account  Note  VRS Hybrid Plan members must make the maximum 4  voluntary contribution to that plan in order to participate in the Cash Match Program  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 